now the Big Bend as Roland Wauer does or have written about it in a more engaging way. This beautifully illustrated book is the perfect companion for a visit to the park, whether in person or by armchair.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aNatural history -- Texas -- Big Bend National Park. 0aNatural historyzTexaszBig Bend National Park. 0aSeasons -- Texas -- Big Bend National Park. 0aSeasonszTexaszBig Bend National Park. 7aNATURE / General.2bisacsh1 aMcGowan, Nancy.40uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/79117640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780292731448423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780292731448/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK